Form990ScheduleAPartVIGrp.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Part V, Section D, Line 8: Distributions To Attentive Supported Organizations
Form990ScheduleAPartVIGrp.ExplanationTxt: IN SUPPORT OF WILLOW ELEMENTARY SCHOOL THE ORGANIZATION PROVIDED $ 481,902 IN MONETARY SUPPORT FOR THE FOLLOWING ACTIVITIES: ASSEMBLIES, CAMPUS IMPROVEMENTS, COMPUTER EQUIPMENT AND SOFTWARE, COMPUTER SPECIALISTS, LANGUAGE ARTS SPECIALISTS, MUSIC SPECIALISTS, PHYSICAL EDUCATION SPECIALISTS, SUBSTITUTE TEACHERS, SPECIAL SCIENCE PROJECTS, INSTRUCTIONAL MATERIALS AND TRAINING, LIBRARY AIDS, MUSIC SUPPLIES, SPECIAL READING PROGRAMS, AIDS FOR THE CLASSROOM AND PLAYGROUND, HOSPITALITY PROGRAMS INCLUDING BROWN BAGS, END OF THE YEAR GIFTS, GREAT WORKS OF ART, HOSTING, SUNSHINE, AND TRUNK OR TREAT. IN ADDITION $ 7,567 WAS SPENT TO COVER ASSOCIATED ADMINISTRATIVE EXPENSES INCLUDING INSURANCE, FILING FEES AND TAXES, BANK AND CREDIT CARD CHARGES, AND OFFICE EXPENSES.
